desc_long							评测						“It's a real hoot that everyone can enjoy!​”Otaku Maker												关于这款游戏							State of Anarchy is a casual take on the top-down crime simulator! Fulfill your inner sociopath as you mow down enemies with guns and cars alike, in a bid to pull off the world's largest heist!State of Anarchy, formerly known as 'Crisis' won the coveted 'Global Game Jam 2015'!http://globalgamejam.org/2015/games/crisis"Annoyingly enjoyable. I laughed in spite of myself""Looks and plays like the imagination of a small child. In a good way"'State of Anarchy' features: 10 weapons 15 enemies Character Development System 2 game modes: Normal (progress is saved after each level) and Hardcore (higher difficulty, no savegames). The Town of enemies and dark humour!						
